<h2>How Quota Works</h2>

<div class="card">

<p>
Each player receives a quota number based on handicap or skill level.
</p>

<p>
Players earn points during the round:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Bogey = 1 point</li>
<li>Par = 2 points</li>
<li>Birdie = 4 points</li>
<li>Eagle = 8 points</li>
</ul>

<p>
At the end of the round:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Beat your quota = win money</li>
<li>Miss your quota = lose money</li>
</ul>

<p>
The farther above or below quota you finish, the bigger the payout.
</p>

